# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/
# Cargo.lock IS committed: this workspace builds binaries (server, engine), so
# we pin exact dependency versions for reproducible builds and CI. Without it,
# CI resolves to the newest transitive deps (some of which require a newer
# toolchain than our pinned Rust), which breaks the build.

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds produce these
*.pdb

# SQLite databases (runtime/test artifacts, should not be committed)
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.db.backup

# Log files
*.log 